const textPartsLength = Number($('get all workflow params').first().json.textPartsLength); // максимум длины части
const text = String($('get whole text from TXT file').first().json.text ?? "");        // исходный текст

// --- ЛОГИКА ---
const partsArr = splitBalancedTTS(text, textPartsLength);

// --- ВЫХОД ---
return partsArr.map((partText, partIndex) => ({
  json: {
    partIndex,
    text: partText,
  },
}));

// ================== FUNCTIONS ==================

function splitBalancedTTS(source, limit) {
  if (!limit || limit <= 0) {
    return source && source.trim() ? [source] : [];
  }

  const sents = splitIntoSentencesWithParas(source);

  // 1) Нормализация сверхдлинных предложений
  const normalized = [];
  for (const s of sents) {
    if (s === "\n\n") {
      normalized.push(s);
      continue;
    }
    if (s.length <= limit) {
      normalized.push(s);
      continue;
    }
    let rest = s;
    while (rest.length > limit) {
      const bp = findBreak(rest, limit);
      const chunk = rest.slice(0, bp).trim();
      if (chunk) normalized.push(chunk);
      rest = rest.slice(bp).trim();
    }
    if (rest.trim()) normalized.push(rest.trim());
  }

  const n = normalized.length;
  const pref = new Array(n + 1).fill(0);
  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {
    pref[i + 1] = pref[i] + normalized[i].length;
  }

  const chunkCost = (i, j) => {
    const length = pref[j] - pref[i];
    if (length > limit) return Infinity;
    const slack = limit - length;
    return slack * slack;
  };

  const best = new Array(n + 1).fill(Infinity);
  const nextBreak = new Array(n + 1).fill(-1);
  best[n] = 0;

  for (let i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
    if (normalized[i] === "\n\n") {
      best[i] = best[i + 1];
      nextBreak[i] = i + 1;
      continue;
    }
    let j = i + 1;
    while (j <= n && (pref[j] - pref[i]) <= limit) {
      const cost = chunkCost(i, j) + best[j];
      if (cost < best[i]) {
        best[i] = cost;
        nextBreak[i] = j;
      }
      j++;
    }
  }

  const chunks = [];
  let i = 0;
  while (i < n) {
    let j = nextBreak[i];
    if (j === -1 || j <= i) j = Math.min(n, i + 1);
    const text = normalized.slice(i, j).join("").trim();
    if (text) chunks.push(text);
    i = j;
  }
  return chunks;
}

function splitIntoSentencesWithParas(source) {
  const result = [];
  const paras = source.split(/\n\s*\n/);
  for (let pIdx = 0; pIdx < paras.length; pIdx++) {
    const p = (paras[pIdx] || "").trim();
    if (!p) continue;

    let i = 0;
    const rx = /([.!?…]+[)"»\]]*)(\s+|$)/g;
    const masked = maskTags(p);

    let m;
    while ((m = rx.exec(masked)) !== null) {
      const end = m.index + m[0].length;
      const sent = p.slice(i, end);
      if (sent.trim()) result.push(sent);
      i = end;
    }
    if (i < p.length) {
      const tail = p.slice(i);
      if (tail.trim()) result.push(tail);
    }
    if (pIdx < paras.length - 1) result.push("\n\n");
  }

  // dedupe repeated paragraph separators
  const compact = [];
  for (const cur of result) {
    if (cur === "\n\n" && compact.length && compact[compact.length - 1] === "\n\n") {
      continue;
    }
    compact.push(cur);
  }
  return compact;
}

function findBreak(remaining, limit) {
  const windowText = remaining.slice(0, limit);
  const masked = maskTags(windowText);
  const spans = getTagSpans(remaining);

  let best = -1;
  const rx = /([.!?…]+[)"»\]]?\s)/g;
  let m;
  while ((m = rx.exec(masked)) !== null) {
    best = m.index + m[0].length;
  }

  if (best >= Math.floor(limit * 0.6)) {
    let idx = adjustBreakIndex(best, spans);
    if (idx <= 0) idx = Math.max(1, best);
    return safeBreakIndex(remaining, idx);
  }

  const lastSpace = Math.max(
    masked.lastIndexOf(" "),
    masked.lastIndexOf("\n"),
    masked.lastIndexOf("\t")
  );
  if (lastSpace > 0) {
    let idx = adjustBreakIndex(lastSpace + 1, spans);
    if (idx <= 0) idx = Math.max(1, lastSpace + 1);
    return safeBreakIndex(remaining, idx);
  }

  let idx = adjustBreakIndex(limit, spans);
  if (idx <= 0) {
    if (spans.length && spans[0][0] === 0) idx = spans[0][1];
    if (idx <= 0) idx = 1;
  }
  return safeBreakIndex(remaining, idx);
}

function getTagSpans(text) {
  const spans = [];
  if (!text.includes("[")) return spans;
  let i = 0;
  while (i < text.length) {
    const start = text.indexOf("[", i);
    if (start === -1) break;
    const end = text.indexOf("]", start + 1);
    if (end === -1) {
      spans.push([start, text.length]);
      break;
    }
    spans.push([start, end + 1]); // end exclusive
    i = end + 1;
  }
  return spans;
}

function maskTags(text) {
  if (!text.includes("[")) return text;
  const spans = getTagSpans(text);
  if (!spans.length) return text;
  const chars = text.split("");
  for (const [start, end] of spans) {
    for (let i = start; i < end; i++) chars[i] = "a";
  }
  return chars.join("");
}

function adjustBreakIndex(idx, spans) {
  for (const [start, end] of spans) {
    if (start < idx && idx < end) {
      if (start > 0) return start;
      return end;
    }
  }
  return idx;
}

function safeBreakIndex(s, idx) {
  if (idx > 0 && idx < s.length) {
    const prev = s.charCodeAt(idx - 1);
    const curr = s.charCodeAt(idx);
    if (0xD800 <= prev && prev <= 0xDBFF && 0xDC00 <= curr && curr <= 0xDFFF) {
      idx -= 1;
    }
  }
  if (idx < 0) return 0;
  if (idx > s.length) return s.length;
  return idx;
}

